---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";

import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";

import appScreenshot from "../../images/app-screenshot.png";
import rubyLogo from "../../images/ruby-logo.svg";
import railsLogo from "../../images/rails-logo.svg";
import postgresLogo from "../../images/postgresql-logo.svg";
import christoph from "../../images/christoph.png";
import fritz from "../../images/fritz.jpg";
import wolfgang from "../../images/wolfgang.jpg";
import clemens from "../../images/clemens.jpg";
---

<Layout
  description="Mit Freuden develops custom B2B software that brings joy. From idea to launch, we deliver production-ready web applications and mobile apps with Ruby on Rails and PostgreSQL."
>
  <div>
    <div class="-mt-8 mb-50 sm:mb-60">
      <div
        class="site-logo mb-16 flex items-center justify-start gap-1 sm:mb-30 sm:justify-start md:gap-3"
      >
        <svg
          class="h-18 md:h-24"
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          viewBox="0 0 40 40"
          stroke="url(#grad1)"
        >
          <!-- Square Brackets [ ] - happy eyes ^^ -->
          <defs>
            <linearGradient id="grad1" x1="0%" y1="50%" x2="20%" y2="0%">
              <stop
                offset="0%"
                style="stop-color:var(--color-rose-400);stop-opacity:1"></stop>
              <stop
                offset="100%"
                style="stop-color:var(--color-orange-400);stop-opacity:1"
              ></stop>
            </linearGradient>
          </defs>
          <g>
            <path
              d="M 10 4 L 4 4 L 4 36 L 10 36"
              fill="none"
              stroke-width="1.5"
              stroke-linecap="round"></path>
            <path
              d="M 30 4 L 36 4 L 36 36 L 30 36"
              fill="none"
              stroke-width="1.5"
              stroke-linecap="round"></path>
            <path
              d="M 10 24 Q 20 32 30 24"
              fill="none"
              stroke-width="1.5"
              stroke-linecap="round"></path>
            <path
              d="M 12 18 Q 14 15 16 18"
              stroke-width="1.5"
              stroke-linecap="round"
              fill="none"></path>
            <path
              d="M 24 18 Q 26 15 28 18"
              stroke-width="1.5"
              stroke-linecap="round"
              fill="none"></path>
          </g>
        </svg>
        <h1
          class="inline-block bg-linear-to-tr from-rose-600 via-rose-400 to-orange-300 bg-clip-text text-5xl font-light tracking-tight text-transparent md:text-6xl"
        >
          Mit Freuden
        </h1>
      </div>

      <div class="sm:text-right">
        <p
          class="font-serif text-4xl/tight tracking-tight text-neutral-600 md:text-5xl/tight"
        >
          What brings joy to&nbsp;life?<br />
          Easy: really,
          <span
            class="bg-linear-to-tr from-rose-600 via-rose-400 to-orange-300 bg-clip-text text-transparent"
          >
            <span class="italic">really</span> well-made software.</span
          >
        </p>
        <p
          class="mt-8 font-serif text-4xl/tight tracking-tight text-neutral-600 md:text-5xl/tight"
        >
          And that's what we do.<br />
          For 20 years now.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mx-auto mb-24 max-w-2xl pt-16 lg:mx-0 lg:mb-32 lg:max-w-none">
      <h2
        class="mb-8 font-serif text-4xl tracking-tight text-neutral-600 md:text-5xl"
      >
        But now, about you.
      </h2>

      <p
        class="mb-8 max-w-2xl font-sans text-lg/8 text-pretty text-neutral-600"
      >
        You might recognize this:
      </p>

      <div class="space-y-10">
        <div>
          <h3
            class="mb-2 font-serif text-xl tracking-tight text-neutral-800 md:text-2xl"
          >
            <q>Where do I get full attention?</q>
          </h3>
          <p class="max-w-2xl font-sans text-lg/8 text-pretty text-neutral-600">
            Large agencies juggle dozens of projects simultaneously. With us,
            every developer focuses on <span
              class="bg-linear-to-tr from-rose-600 via-rose-400 to-orange-300 bg-clip-text font-bold text-transparent"
            >
              at most one project at a time</span
            >. That means: full attention, true commitment, fast decisions.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3
            class="mb-2 font-serif text-xl tracking-tight text-neutral-800 md:text-2xl"
          >
            <q>Who helps me get from idea to concrete solution?</q>
          </h3>
          <p class="max-w-2xl font-sans text-lg/8 text-pretty text-neutral-600">
            We don't wait for a finished spec. We understand your problem and
            <span
              class="bg-linear-to-tr from-rose-600 via-rose-400 to-orange-300 bg-clip-text font-bold text-transparent"
            >
              develop the right solution together with you</span
            >. From idea through implementation to launch.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3
            class="mb-2 font-serif text-xl tracking-tight text-neutral-800 md:text-2xl"
          >
            <q>And afterwards? Who really stays by my side long-term?</q>
          </h3>
          <p class="max-w-2xl font-sans text-lg/8 text-pretty text-neutral-600">
            Software lives and needs to adapt – but who stays engaged when
            requirements change? That's why we design software to be flexible
            and extensible from the start, and <span
              class="bg-linear-to-tr from-rose-600 via-rose-400 to-orange-300 bg-clip-text font-bold text-transparent"
              >remain your reliable partner</span
            > as your business evolves.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div
      class="mx-auto mb-24 max-w-2xl pt-16 lg:mx-0 lg:mb-32 lg:max-w-none"
      id="team"
    >
      <h2
        class="mb-8 font-serif text-4xl tracking-tight text-neutral-600 md:text-5xl"
      >
        Four experienced developers. A direct line.
      </h2>

      <p class="max-w-2xl font-sans text-lg/8 text-pretty text-neutral-600">
        With us, you speak directly with the people who know your project inside
        and out. No account managers, no hierarchies, no telephone game.
      </p>

      <ul
        role="list"
        class="mt-16 grid grid-cols-1 gap-y-16 md:grid-cols-2 md:gap-x-12 lg:mx-0 lg:max-w-none"
      >
        <li>
          <Image
            loading="lazy"
            src={clemens}
            alt=""
            class="aspect-square w-32 rounded-full object-cover outline-1 -outline-offset-1 outline-black/5"
            width="128"
          />
          <h3 class="mt-6 text-lg/8 font-semibold text-gray-900 sm:text-xl/8">
            Clemens Helm
          </h3>
          <p class="mt-4 text-lg/8 text-pretty text-gray-600 lg:text-base/7">
            Clemens brings CTO and VP Engineering experience to helping teams
            rescue their Rails applications. With 20+ years in full-stack
            development, he focuses on performance optimization, security
            hardening, and long-term maintainability, turning legacy codebases
            into clean, reliable foundations that teams enjoy working with
            again.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <Image
            loading="lazy"
            src={christoph}
            alt=""
            class="aspect-square w-32 rounded-full object-cover outline-1 -outline-offset-1 outline-black/5"
            width="128"
          />
          <h3
            class="mt-6 text-lg/8 font-semibold text-neutral-900 sm:text-xl/8"
          >
            Christoph Lupprich
          </h3>
          <p class="mt-4 text-lg/8 text-pretty text-neutral-600 lg:text-base/7">
            With 15+ years building full-stack web applications, Christoph
            specializes in Ruby, Ruby on Rails, and PostgreSQL. From maritime
            safety systems to geospatial data processing, he's passionate about
            solving real business problems and bringing products to life from
            day one.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <Image
            loading="lazy"
            src={fritz}
            alt=""
            class="aspect-square w-32 rounded-full object-cover outline-1 -outline-offset-1 outline-black/5"
            width="128"
          />
          <h3
            class="mt-6 text-lg/8 font-semibold text-neutral-900 sm:text-xl/8"
          >
            Fritz Grabo
          </h3>
          <p class="mt-4 text-lg/8 text-pretty text-neutral-600 lg:text-base/7">
            Fritz brings 20+ years of experience in backend architecture and
            scaling web applications. He's mission-driven, focusing on
            meaningful problems while maintaining the balance between rapid
            development and robust infrastructure—from root servers to modern
            cloud solutions.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <Image
            loading="lazy"
            src={wolfgang}
            alt=""
            class="aspect-square w-32 rounded-full object-cover outline-1 -outline-offset-1 outline-black/5"
            width="128"
          />
          <h3
            class="mt-6 text-lg/8 font-semibold text-neutral-900 sm:text-xl/8"
          >
            Wolfgang Rittner
          </h3>
          <p class="mt-4 text-lg/8 text-pretty text-neutral-600 lg:text-base/7">
            A hands-on software architect with 20+ years under his belt,
            Wolfgang excels at cutting through complexity and delivering
            practical solutions. He jumps in to understand system interactions
            and provide actionable insights that unblock and accelerate
            projects.
          </p>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div
      class="mx-auto mb-24 max-w-2xl pt-16 lg:mx-0 lg:mb-32 lg:max-w-none"
      id="solutions"
    >
      <h2
        class="mb-8 font-serif text-4xl tracking-tight text-neutral-600 md:text-5xl"
      >
        How we work
      </h2>

      <div class="space-y-10">
        <div>
          <h3
            class="mb-2 font-serif text-xl tracking-tight text-neutral-800 md:text-2xl"
          >
            The foundation: 20 years of experience
          </h3>
          <p class="max-w-2xl font-sans text-lg/8 text-pretty text-neutral-600">
            Vibe-coding a prototype is easy – developing reliable software that
            stays in production for years is a different story. We've learned
            what makes <span
              class="bg-linear-to-tr from-rose-600 via-rose-400 to-orange-300 bg-clip-text font-bold text-transparent"
              >flexible, resilient systems</span
            >, and what makes projects successful in the long run.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3
            class="mb-2 font-serif text-xl tracking-tight text-neutral-800 md:text-2xl"
          >
            Your requirements, your software
          </h3>
          <p class="max-w-2xl font-sans text-lg/8 text-pretty text-neutral-600">
            <span
              class="bg-linear-to-tr from-rose-600 via-rose-400 to-orange-300 bg-clip-text font-bold text-transparent"
              >We take the time to truly understand</span
            > to truly understand your processes and challenges. Only when we understand
            what you need do we develop the best solution together with you.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3
            class="mb-2 font-serif text-xl tracking-tight text-neutral-800 md:text-2xl"
          >
            One developer, one project
          </h3>
          <p class="max-w-2xl font-sans text-lg/8 text-pretty text-neutral-600">
            Every developer focuses on at most one project at a time. That
            means: direct communication, deep understanding of your context, and
            <span
              class="bg-linear-to-tr from-rose-600 via-rose-400 to-orange-300 bg-clip-text font-bold text-transparent"
              >true responsibility for the outcome</span
            >.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3
            class="mb-2 font-serif text-xl tracking-tight text-neutral-800 md:text-2xl"
          >
            Built for today and tomorrow
          </h3>
          <p class="max-w-2xl font-sans text-lg/8 text-pretty text-neutral-600">
            We think in years, not sprints. Our solutions are designed from the
            start to <span
              class="bg-linear-to-tr from-rose-600 via-rose-400 to-orange-300 bg-clip-text font-bold text-transparent"
              >grow with your requirements</span
            >
            – technically solid, maintainable, and extensible.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

